title: Project for an octagonal ceiling: Olympus
medium: Brush and black and gray gouche, pen and black ink, black chalk, white heightening on paper
description: Inscribed in a square.  Top:  The seated Diana converses with Jupiter; Apollo stands between the two.  Bottom:  the flyng Hermes puts his right hand on the left leg of the seated Venus.  A putto carriesthe broken bow of Cupid away.
